Text.string: Got me a job here 'bout a witch. Up to no good, I'd wager.

Well hay there. I'm Murl, spelled like “hurl”. Warlock of the seventh aleph, and practitioner of the fiery arts. Gots me a right problem with this witch lives down bog-way. I think she broke... the Pact. Need you to go help her out with some chores an' see if you can't find out what she's up to.
Ah, yes—you've got enough swamp blooms for my, uh... purposes. Hnhnhnhahahah...
You jus' hang on to them there red-caps for a minute. I'll put 'em to good use in a tick-tock or two.
Now do me a kindness, dear, and drop those shrooms right into my Double-Double™-brand Trouble Cauldron. Hahahaha...
Gahahahaha! With these blooms... my minions will be more powerful than ever! All hail the Calypsos! My dark masters.
Go, my minions! Show them the power of Azalea's Brew!

She betrayed... the Pact! Well, nothin' for it now but to take her out! That gate's hexed real good, but ol' Murl foresaw this dark turn. Bring me them extra swamp bloom, and we'll take care of that burly gate.
Now it ain't no wonder why she broke her vows to... the Pact. Worshippin' them Siren twins is a clear violation of our arcane mandates and such.
Few moons back, I figured out how to make a righteous boom-brew in this here cauldron! Drop them red-caps in there an' staaand back.

Hahaha! Told ya! Now I went 'n' packed some of that boom-brew down in this here 'nade-chucker. Should help you break into her bog, destroy her cauldrons, and rid us 'a that foul witch once and fer good!
Now, go git 'er! Those who turn from... the Pact... must be punished with excommunication from life! Also known as “death”.

Her name's Azalea Splinters. A right crazybird, that one. I need you to figure out whether she done broked her vow to the Pact we's in—and that's Pact with a capital “P”, mind you. Super secret heavy occult stuff.
Careful down there! Been seein' all manner of strange frightfuls comin' and goin' outta her place on the recent.
Begone! You are not worthy to tread upon this hallowed ground! Minions! Destroy the Vault Thief!
You'll pay for these trespasses, Vault Thief!
Keep it up and you'll have to face ME! I'll skin you alive for the God-Queen!
I'm warning you, Vault Thief! Just leave now and I might let you live!
That's enough!
Haaaa-haha! Oh, you done made 'er mad now!
Dark are the forces that await you. The mud beckons! The high night calls! From the broken sky I will sear you with hellfire itself! For I am Azalea, mistress of the bog, and I am... your DOOM!
What a drama queen.
Also—and this is neither here nor there, mind ya—but she always brought the worst cookies to... the Pact's... weekly stitch-'n'-bitch.
And thus is the fate of all who stray from... the Pact. Me and mine can't possibly thank you enough for riddin' us o' that awful wench of a witch. I got somethin' for ya as thanks. Come 'n' get it.
Now I infused that boom-brew down into this grenade mod. Hope you like it! You sure showed that bitch what-for! I mean “witch”. Wait, what did I say? Aw hell, who cares. SHE DEAD! Hahahahaha!
Hey! Heard you need help with somethin'?
Um, hello? Heard you need some help.
I have heard you require assistance.
Heyyyy—heard you need a spot of help.
Well, here you go, Vault Hunter. You sure showed that bitch what-for! I mean “witch”. Wait, what did I say? Aw hell, who cares, SHE DEAD! Hahahaha!
That's right! I know who you are! Go suck a bog branch, VAULT THIEF!

We warlocks of the seventh aleph, we worship the crushing bone, the night splinter, the ones who wait beneath the mud. But worshipping two social media stars... well, there are some dark paths ol' Murl will not follow.
Ahhh, you must be the new errand runner I called for. Excellent. Heh-heh-heh!
You just play it cool, Vault Hunter. Her being a right powerful dark practitioner and all.

Gather some green swamp bloom mushrooms so that I might perfect my brew. My little truffle hunter, Pippie, will show you where to find them. But Pippie still don't know the difference between the green mushrooms and the red ones. Only bring me the green ones, okay, dear?
Now come on back for... the brewing ritual.

Aw, dang, she got you out pickin' them green swamp bloomers? Well, while you're at it, could you pick some a' them red-cap blooms for me? If Azalea did done broke... the Pact... yer gonna want some of them before this is all over. Trust ol' Murl on that.
Ah, yes—the area is crawling with salivatin' saurians. Good huntin', heh-heh-heh...
